# ğŸ“š English TTS Batch Generator for Anki

Generate **natural-sounding English audio** from text files using **Microsoft Edge Neural TTS**, and automatically create an **Anki-ready CSV** for efficient listening, shadowing, and repetition practice.

This project is designed for **English learners and developers** who want a **free, high-quality, and fully automated** way to build audio-based study materials.

---

## âœ¨ Features

* ğŸ”Š **High-quality Neural TTS** (Microsoft Edge voices)
* ğŸ“‚ **Batch processing** of multiple `.txt` files
* ğŸ§ **Sentence-level MP3 output** (perfect for shadowing)
* ğŸ§  **Anki import-ready CSV** generation
* â™»ï¸ **Resume-safe** (skips already generated audio)
* âš™ï¸ **Configurable speech rate and voice**
* ğŸ’¯ **Free to use** (no API keys required)

