## ğŸ’¡ Recommended Study Workflow

* ğŸ§ **Listening**: Passive listening while commuting
* ğŸ—£ **Shadowing**: Speak along with audio
* âœï¸ **Dictation**: Pause â†’ write â†’ check
* ğŸ§  **Anki Review**: Audio-first recall

---

## âš ï¸ Notes & Limitations

* Edge TTS relies on online services; heavy usage may trigger rate limits.
* A small delay is intentionally added between requests to avoid throttling.
* This project is **not affiliated with Microsoft**.

